  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      New ESC 2015 recommendations with encouragement to set up a Multidisciplinary Consultation
      Meeting to discuss the medical and surgical management of endocarditis, set up at Strasbourg
      University Hospital in October 2016: Impact and benefits
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
